title: How to Style a High and Tight | AXE | Instagroom
description:
Joshua keeps his high and tight real tight to show off his tattoos. 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream 
Curl sponge

THE STEPS:
1. Mix cream 
2. Scrunch into hair
3. Sponge to achieve a curly texture

transcripts: I do think style’s important. It’s a way of showing people a bit about myself before they meet me. I’ll take a small scoop of cream. Scrunch it into my hair. Then I’ll take a sponge, slowly twist it in to give it a nice texture, beautiful.
